{
  "stem": "6009.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Then they're going to come and kill us.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So the war still going on there between Poland and Germany.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We were in the middle.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I said, if it's a God someplace, why don't fall in a bomb here.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we should be killed, not waiting till the Germans come and shoot us.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that took about an hour or so.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The shooting stopped outside.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then the door opened up.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they come in, about 20 of them with machine guns and bayonets on.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And one was an officer with a revolver.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he's like, you Polish pigs, you'll be all killed.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he hollered on us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH] camp, prisoner of war camp, took us I think another 10 days.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This was camp-- that was January 4th.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "January 4th we became imprisoned, or January 5th.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the [NON-ENGLISH], first [NON-ENGLISH] we came to the camp.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There was not yet a camp, the regular camp.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was just Germany brought us in barracks.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was not a real camp.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The real camp took another two camps.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There was Stalag II B",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "How long I've been there?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Since 1940 in March.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They didn't give a shower, no nothing.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we was living with bugs and everything.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then they decided to liberate us from camps and send us on to Poland.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Stalag II B.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The city close to it was Hammerstein.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Up to March, 1940.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In 1940s, took us out to say we get liberated, to send us home to Poland, we go free.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it was looking suspicious, but nothing we could do.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They put us-- they took us in our showers.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They could make us clean, and gave us new uniforms, Polish uniforms, brand new ones, everything.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
